V0205_01_00_00_0.text:
Power Tool Dragon!
Let's show 'em we're the ultimate duo!

V0205_01_00_01_0.text: Don't wanna brag, but my deck is pretty awesome!

V0205_01_00_02_0.text:
You're lucky!
You get to see how cool my monsters are!

V0205_01_00_03_0.text: I'll prove why I'm a member of the greatest Duel crew!

V0205_01_00_04_0.text:
Yusei! 
You gotta check out how much tougher I am now!

V0205_01_00_05_0.text: Jack, I won't let your Power Deck push me over!

V0205_01_00_06_0.text: If I defeat you, am I the best Duelist at Duel Academy?

V0205_01_00_07_0.text: Your tricks may be tricky, but they won't fool me!

V0205_01_00_08_0.text:
Luna!
Your bro's gonna reach the top!

V0205_01_00_09_0.text:
Officer Trudge...
Are your skills as scary as your face?

V0205_01_00_10_0.text: I won't let you hurt Luna!

V0205_01_00_10_1.text: It's my role as her big bro to save her from you!

V0205_01_00_11_0.text: I'd be lying if I said my knees weren't shaking...

V0205_01_00_11_1.text: But I promised to protect Luna, so that's what I'll do!

V0205_03_00_04_0.text: I gotta stay calm and find a way to win!

V0205_03_00_05_0.text:
Not gonna cry...
I know there's still hope!

V0205_04_00_02_0.text:
Let me be lucky, just this once...
I draw!

V0205_05_00_00_0.text: C'mon... Give me the power to protect the ones I love!

V0205_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my face-down card!

V0205_08_00_00_0.text: I equip Morphtronic Cord on a Morphtronic monster!

V0205_08_00_01_0.text: You're about to feel Morphtronic Cord's effect!

V0205_08_00_01_1.text: By changing battle position, a Spell or Trap's a goner!

V0205_08_00_02_0.text:
Morphtronic Accelerator!
I return a Morphtronic to my deck!

V0205_08_00_02_1.text: That lets me destroy a card on the field and draw a new one!

V0205_08_00_05_0.text: The Equip Spell, Morphtronic Repair Unit!

V0205_08_00_06_0.text: My Equip Spell, Morphtronic Rusty Engine!

V0205_08_00_07_1.text: I use Junk Box to Special Summon a Morphtronic monster!

V0205_08_00_08_0.text: The Equip Spell, Double Tool C&D!

V0205_08_00_09_0.text:
I use my Quick-Play Spell!
Twister!

V0205_08_00_11_0.text:
I'll use my Equip Spell!
Break! Draw!!

V0205_08_00_14_0.text: Here comes my big winning combo!

V0205_08_00_14_1.text: I equip the Equip Spell, Megamorph!

V0205_08_00_16_0.text:
I activate my Quick-Play Spell!
Factory of 100 Machines!

V0205_08_00_18_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Morphtronics, Scramble!!

V0205_08_00_20_0.text:
I activate my Counter Trap!
Morphtronic Forcefield!

V0205_08_00_21_0.text: I activate my Trap Card, Morphtransition!

V0205_08_00_21_1.text: Your attack's negated, and my Morphtronic changes position!

V0205_08_00_22_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Power Break!

V0205_08_00_23_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Power-Up Adapter!

V0205_08_00_24_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Morphtronic Mix-up!

V0205_08_00_25_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Urgent Tuning!

V0205_08_00_26_0.text:
My Counter Trap activates!
Dark Bribe!

V0205_08_00_28_0.text: My monster equipped with this can zero out damage!

V0205_08_00_29_0.text: The Equip Spell, Pain to Power!

V0205_08_00_30_0.text:
You're in for it now!
Pain to Power's effect activates!

V0205_08_00_31_0.text: As long as I have a single Life Point, I won't give up!

V0205_08_00_31_1.text: I activate the Spell Card, Double Ripple!

V0205_08_00_31_2.text: I call out Power Tool Dragon and Ancient Fairy Dragon!

V0205_09_00_04_1.text: I can Special Summon a Level 4 Morphtronic from my hand!

V0205_09_00_05_0.text: Here's Staplen's effect while in Attack Position!

V0205_09_00_06_0.text: Here's Staplen's effect while in Defense Position!

V0205_09_00_11_0.text: Check out Slingen's Attack Position effect!

V0205_09_00_12_0.text: Here's Magnen Bar's Attack Position effect!

V0205_09_00_13_0.text: I'll use Celfon's Attack Position effect!

V0205_09_00_14_0.text: I'll use Celfon's Defense Position effect!

V0205_09_00_16_1.text: When a Morphtronic is attacked, I can negate that attack!

V0205_09_00_17_0.text: I'm using Remoten's Attack Position effect!

V0205_09_00_18_0.text: I'm using Remoten's Defense Position effect!

V0205_09_00_19_1.text: I add a Morphtronic Spell or Trap in my grave to my hand!

V0205_09_00_20_0.text: I'm gonna use Gadget Hauler's effect!

V0205_09_00_21_0.text: I'll toss Gadget Driver to the grave to activate its effect!

V0205_09_00_23_0.text: By Synchro Summoning Life Stream Dragon, I have 4000 LP!

V0205_09_00_24_0.text: By equipping an Equip Spell, Power Tool lets me draw!

V0205_09_00_25_0.text: Power Tool can steal an Equip Card!

V0205_09_00_26_1.text: I Special Summon a Level 4 or lower monster from my hand!

V0205_09_00_28_1.text: When a Field Spell activates on my turn, I draw a card!

V0205_09_00_29_0.text: With a Field in play, Ancient Pixie Dragon uses its effect!

V0205_09_00_29_1.text: I get to destroy a monster in Attack Position!

V0205_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0205_13_00_04_0.text: I'm counting on ya, Morphtronic Staplen!

V0205_13_00_10_0.text: Come on out, Morphtronic Magnen Bar!

V0205_13_00_17_0.text: Let's do this thing, Gadget Arms!

V0205_37_00_00_0.text: Machine and might combine to bring peace to the world!

V0205_13_00_20_0.text:
The monster with some major motor!
Power Tool Dragon!

V0205_37_00_01_0.text: Courage and power lead to a revolution for peace!

V0205_37_00_02_0.text: If you wanna feel the steel, be my guest!

V0205_13_00_23_0.text: I'd rather have Machines in my deck, but...

V0205_13_00_23_1.text:
Whatever! It's allll good!
Comrade Swordsman of Landstar!

V0205_37_00_03_0.text: The magic that lives in each creature merge and become one!

V0205_37_00_04_0.text: The spirit of the ancient forest takes solid form!

V0205_19_00_21_0.text:
I'm not giving up hope!
Life Stream Dragon attacks!

V0205_19_00_22_0.text: I'll attack with Power Tool Mecha Dragon!

V0205_19_00_24_0.text: Help me out, Ancient Fairy Dragon!

V0205_21_00_02_0.text: I just have to keep believing in my cards...

V0205_28_00_00_0.text:
Hooray!
This is the best feeling ever!

V0205_28_00_01_0.text:
It's my job to protect Luna!
So I gotta get tough!

V0205_28_00_02_0.text: I know how badly you want to win.

V0205_28_00_02_1.text:
Because I feel the same.
That's why I can't lose either!

V0205_28_00_03_0.text:
My dream is to Turbo Duel against Yusei and Jack!
And win!

V0205_28_00_04_0.text:
Yusei, you believe in yourself.
So I decided I would too!

V0205_28_00_05_0.text: I'm gonna be as cool as you, Jack!

V0205_28_00_05_1.text: Even if you're not the King anymore, you're still cool...

V0205_28_00_06_0.text:
I defeated Akiza!
I'll rule the school in no time!

V0205_28_00_07_0.text: Maybe I should take your spot on Team 5D's!

V0205_28_00_08_0.text:
You thought I was awesome?
Aww...

V0205_28_00_09_0.text: See? Adults aren't always better than kids!

V0205_28_00_09_1.text: Me and Power Tool Dragon dealt you justice!

V0205_28_00_10_0.text: Even if I make a fool of myself, I'll protect Luna!

V0205_28_00_11_0.text: As long as I'm alive, I'm not giving up!

V0205_29_00_00_0.text:
Sigh...
I can't win with this deck.

V0205_29_00_01_0.text:
Aww!
If I drew this one turn earlier, I would've won!

V0205_29_00_02_0.text: I gotta get better if I'm gonna be Luna's hero!

V0205_29_00_04_0.text: I'm not the best yet, but my friends will help me improve!

V0205_29_00_05_1.text: I'll be as strong as you someday!

V0205_29_00_06_0.text:
That's why you get the best grades.
I never had a chance.

V0205_29_00_07_0.text:
You really are tricky!
I couldn't predict any of your moves!

V0205_29_00_08_0.text:
Sigh...
I'm such a bad brother...

V0205_29_00_09_0.text: I thought you'd be a bum, but boy was I wrong.

V0205_29_00_10_0.text: If I lose now, Luna will be...

V0205_29_00_11_1.text: I can't just watch from the sidelines!

V0205_30_00_01_0.text: This is why I never wanna grow up.

V0205_34_00_01_0.text: My deck has no chance against yours.

V0205_34_00_02_0.text: I can't think of any more strategies!

V0205_34_00_07_0.text: As long as I'm breathin', I'm not giving up!

V0205_34_00_08_0.text:
What will today's card be?
This one!

V0205_32_00_01_0.text:
Which app will I play today?
This one!
Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Links! Yeah!
Let's win again today!

V0205_35_00_00_0.text: It's my dream to be the King!

V0205_35_00_01_0.text: Who's on the mightiest team in the game? Me!

V0205_36_00_03_0.text: Aww, I wanted to win before it was your turn, Luna.

V0205_36_00_04_0.text:
You can do it, Luna!
I believe in you!

V0205_36_00_05_0.text:
Sorry...
I kept saying I'd save you, but...

V0205_36_00_06_0.text: I've set 'em up, so you can knock 'em down!

V0205_36_00_07_0.text: I'll do my best to help, so I know you got this!

V0205_36_00_08_0.text:
We haven't lost yet!
Don't give up hope!
